### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### Text chat (no audio)
POST http://localhost:3000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Hey Oxcy, what's good?",
  "userId": "test-user"
}

###

### Text chat with TTS audio
POST http://localhost:3000/chat?tts=true
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Set a reminder to call mum at 6pm",
  "userId": "test-user"
}

###

### Save a memory manually
POST http://localhost:3000/memory
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "test-user",
  "content": "User's name is Somto. Works in tech. Lives in London."
}

###

### Read memories
GET http://localhost:3000/memory/test-user

###

### Audio upload (use curl — see README)
# curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/process-audio \
#   -H "user-id: test-user" \
#   -F "audio=@/path/to/test.wav"
